2026-05-13T20:28:54.8439149Z 13    <!--
2026-05-13T20:28:54.8439561Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-13T20:28:54.8440224Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
