2026-05-13T20:28:55.1125800Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T20:28:55.1126054Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T20:28:55.1126290Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
